{"tid":2358945,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"逾五成受訪護士有意移民　護協憂青黃不接促增加護士學額","createTime":"2021-01-08T13:24:28.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-08T14:16:06.000Z","uid":39464,"like":8,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"813f918cfacb543ab34369360977188f4da4ba19","tid":2358945,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T13:24:28.000Z","msg":"香港護士協會今（8日）公布護士移民意向調查，結果顯示，逾五成受訪者正辦理或考慮移民，當中逾九成人因政治及社會影響決定移民。護協主席源志敏形容這次移民潮「好似返咗97年」，擔心行內人手不足及青黃不接，促政府加開護士學額及改善薪酬待遇。<br />\n<br />\n護協去年11月訪問684名護士，有六成受訪者受聘於醫管局。結果顯示，9.9%受訪者正辦理移民手續，當中八成會在兩年內離開香港、43.9%正考慮移民，而46.2%則不會移民。最熱門的移民國家為英國及澳洲。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/20210108/s00001/1610108944270/%e9%80%be%e4%ba%94%e6%88%90%e5%8f%97%e8%a8%aa%e8%ad%b7%e5%a3%ab%e6%9c%89%e6%84%8f%e7%a7%bb%e6%b0%91-%e8%ad%b7%e5%8d%94%e6%86%82%e9%9d%92%e9%bb%83%e4%b8%8d%e6%8e%a5%e4%bf%83%e5%a2%9e%e5%8a%a0%e8%ad%b7%e5%a3%ab%e5%ad%b8%e9%a1%8d\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20210108%2Fs00001%2F1610108944270%2F%25e9%2580%25be%25e4%25ba%2594%25e6%2588%2590%25e5%258f%2597%25e8%25a8%25aa%25e8%25ad%25b7%25e5%25a3%25ab%25e6%259c%2589%25e6%2584%258f%25e7%25a7%25bb%25e6%25b0%2591-%25e8%25ad%25b7%25e5%258d%2594%25e6%2586%2582%25e9%259d%2592%25e9%25bb%2583%25e4%25b8%258d%25e6%258e%25a5%25e4%25bf%2583%25e5%25a2%259e%25e5%258a%25a0%25e8%25ad%25b7%25e5%25a3%25ab%25e5%25ad%25b8%25e9%25a1%258d&d=vGGWHGA7%2F8HunCPhnXLTIdXOzSaib9VKtZEsb4jNOpA%3D&h=207c2980\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20210108%2Fs00001%2F1610108944270%2F%25e9%2580%25be%25e4%25ba%2594%25e6%2588%2590%25e5%258f%2597%25e8%25a8%25aa%25e8%25ad%25b7%25e5%25a3%25ab%25e6%259c%2589%25e6%2584%258f%25e7%25a7%25bb%25e6%25b0%2591-%25e8%25ad%25b7%25e5%258d%2594%25e6%2586%2582%25e9%259d%2592%25e9%25bb%2583%25e4%25b8%258d%25e6%258e%25a5%25e4%25bf%2583%